<plot>Johnny Gallagher, a sergeant, is sent with a prisoner from Germany. The prisoner escapes in the men's room at National Airport and Hackman begins his search for his man. Enlisting the help of his ex wife and various old friends he finds that the prisoner is part of a plot by senior military figures on both sides to kill a very high-ranking world figure in order to sabotage arms control talks.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581143</url></doc>
